---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Swimming Pool Area — Mas du Chanoine" description="Heated 12m x 6m mosaic swimming pool with views of Saint-Paul de Vence. Sunbeds, parasols and relaxation area at Mas du Chanoine." lang="en">
  <section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/70 via-primary-950/30 to-primary-950/10 z-10"></div>
    <img src="/media/piscine/vue-montagne.jpg" alt="The swimming pool at Mas du Chanoine with views of Saint-Paul de Vence" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
    <div class="relative z-20 text-white px-4 md:px-8 pb-12 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-3 text-primary-200 font-light">40ft × 20ft · Heated in season</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold leading-tight">Swimming Pool Area</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Relaxation</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Pool & Relaxation</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>The 12m x 6m (40ft x 20ft) swimming pool is located in an area surrounded by a hedge of shrubs and multicolored flowers. This space ensures privacy.</p><p>Whether you want to swim or just rest, you will enjoy this area of relaxation. Pool towels are at your disposal in every guest room.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Comfort</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Sunbeds & Parasols</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>Sunbeds, tables and parasols are located around the pool. You can choose to settle in the shade of the palm tree on the lawn or you may prefer the warmth of the sun's rays.</p><p>From your deckchair, you can appreciate the delicate outlines of the parasol pine tree.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Features</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Mosaic & Heated Pool</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>The 12m x 6m swimming pool lined with genuine OPIO mosaic tiles has a depth ranging from 1.20m to 2.20m. Its originality can be seen in the soft green colour.</p><p>The water is heated in season (according to outdoor temperatures, from May 1st to September 30th). South facing, the pool area enjoys sunshine all day. For security reasons, the pool gate is locked at night.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Evening</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Village & Hill Views</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>In the evening, the village of Saint-Paul de Vence, in its setting of hills and mountains, its ramparts and the illuminated steeple of the church, will truly delight you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-4">Dive into serenity</h2>
      <p class="text-primary-300 mb-8 text-lg">Book your stay and enjoy the pool at Mas du Chanoine.</p>
      <a href="https://masduchanoine.thais-hotel.com/hotel/website/reservations.php?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-100">Book now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
